oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Fan Fair radio spots - CMA various artists - 1973
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Various Country Music Fan Fair promotional radio spots from 1973, featuring Jeanne Pruett, Tommy Cash, Leroy Van Dyke, Conway Twitty, Loretta Lynn, Darryl Reeves, Anne Murray, Donna Fargo, Bobby G. Rice, Jerry Clower, George Jones, Tammy Wynette, Jeannie Seely, Jack Greene, and Charlie Louvin.
